  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>POSSESS. ADAPT. SURVIVE.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Memory Lost, a thrilling fast-paced cyberpunk-style top-dawn shooter where you are not just fighting enemies — you <strong>become</strong> them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/60fb2c7c3e9b574b14791baa534d66cd.poster.avif?t=1748885445\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/60fb2c7c3e9b574b14791baa534d66cd.webm?t=1748885445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/60fb2c7c3e9b574b14791baa534d66cd.mp4?t=1748885445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A CYBERPUNK NIGHTMARE</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the sprawling, dystopian city of <strong>Detraxis</strong>, ruthless corporations rule, conducting inhumane experiments on the helpless. You are an AI, created by <strong>RedSky Corporation</strong>, now fighting to overthrow your own creators. But in this brutal world, survival demands more than just firepower—it requires intelligence, strategy, and the ability to <strong>seize control of your enemies</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/2eb75fba0b41eae58d32a90c745f778d.poster.avif?t=1748885445\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/2eb75fba0b41eae58d32a90c745f778d.webm?t=1748885445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/2eb75fba0b41eae58d32a90c745f778d.mp4?t=1748885445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BODY-SHIFTING COMBAT</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget traditional combat — <strong>your body is your greatest weapon</strong>. As a digital entity, you can <strong>possess enemies</strong>, instantly adapting their skills, weapons, and abilities. Jump from host to host in rapid succession, combining <strong>77 unique weapons</strong>and devastating melee attacks to wipe out your foes.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Control and switch between enemies</strong> in real time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>60 enemy types & 10 powerful bosses</strong>, each with unique abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Five upgrade trees</strong> to customize your playstyle</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/d324ccb72139dd4c222ff258cbb6d753.poster.avif?t=1748885445\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/d324ccb72139dd4c222ff258cbb6d753.webm?t=1748885445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/d324ccb72139dd4c222ff258cbb6d753.mp4?t=1748885445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A WORLD OF SECRETS & CHOICES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Memory Lost</i> offers more than just action — it delivers a <strong>deep, choice-driven narrative</strong> with <strong>three different endings</strong>. Your decisions will shape the fate of Detraxis.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a rich cyberpunk world</strong>, divided into diverse hubs and levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engage with unique NPCs</strong> and uncover hidden stories — some tragic, some darkly humorous</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hack, infiltrate, and outsmart your foes</strong> to uncover the truth behind RedSky’s experiments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hand-drawn animated cutscenes</strong> bring the world to life</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/5a7c4841df853f2e2c1b62628b37186f.poster.avif?t=1748885445\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/5a7c4841df853f2e2c1b62628b37186f.webm?t=1748885445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/5a7c4841df853f2e2c1b62628b37186f.mp4?t=1748885445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control the minds of your enemies, and rewrite your destiny. The future of Detraxis is in your hands. Will you break free, or will you be just another lost memory?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>POSSESS. ADAPT. SURVIVE.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Memory Lost, a thrilling fast-paced cyberpunk-style top-dawn shooter where you are not just fighting enemies — you <strong>become</strong> them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/60fb2c7c3e9b574b14791baa534d66cd.poster.avif?t=1748885445\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/60fb2c7c3e9b574b14791baa534d66cd.webm?t=1748885445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/60fb2c7c3e9b574b14791baa534d66cd.mp4?t=1748885445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A CYBERPUNK NIGHTMARE</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the sprawling, dystopian city of <strong>Detraxis</strong>, ruthless corporations rule, conducting inhumane experiments on the helpless. You are an AI, created by <strong>RedSky Corporation</strong>, now fighting to overthrow your own creators. But in this brutal world, survival demands more than just firepower—it requires intelligence, strategy, and the ability to <strong>seize control of your enemies</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/2eb75fba0b41eae58d32a90c745f778d.poster.avif?t=1748885445\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/2eb75fba0b41eae58d32a90c745f778d.webm?t=1748885445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/