paragraph\" ><strong>Engage with unique NPCs</strong> and uncover hidden stories — some tragic, some darkly humorous</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hack, infiltrate, and outsmart your foes</strong> to uncover the truth behind RedSky’s experiments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hand-drawn animated cutscenes</strong> bring the world to life</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/5a7c4841df853f2e2c1b62628b37186f.poster.avif?t=1748885445\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/5a7c4841df853f2e2c1b62628b37186f.webm?t=1748885445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483190/extras/5a7c4841df853f2e2c1b62628b37186f.mp4?t=1748885445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control the minds of your enemies, and rewrite your destiny. The future of Detraxis is in your hands. Will you break free, or will you be just another lost memory?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
